Package cscie160.project

Interface Summary
Account Interface that defines a remote Bank object
ATM Defines the interface for an ATM object
ATMFactory Defines the interface for getting an ATM remote object
ATMListener Defines the event listener for an ATM object
BankFactory Interface that defines a remote Bank object
Security Defines the interface for a Security object
 

Class Summary
AccountImpl Creates an account to hold a balance that can be credited and debited
AccountInfo The AccountInfo object is a data class that includes an account number and a PIN.
AccountPermissions Creates permissions to perform transactions on an account (deposit, withdraw, get balance)
ATMFactoryImpl ATM Factory Implementation
ATMImpl Implements the ATM interface
ATMServer Creates an instance of the atmfactory, exports it and registers it with the RMI registry.
BankImpl Creates a bank object that hosts remote Account objects
BankServer Creates an instance of the Bank and Security objects, exports it and registers it with the RMI registry.
Client Creates a Client that connects to a server.
SecurityImpl Authorizes and authenticates AccountInfo objects
TransactionNotification Displays a message that a transaction has been made
 

Enum Summary
Permissions Enumerated list of transaction types
 

Exception Summary
ATMEmptyException Customer exception when the ATM does not have enough cash on hand
AuthAcctException Customer exception when an account does not have the proper permissions to perform a transaction
AuthPinException Customer exception when a PIN does not match
InsufficientFundsException Customer exception when the account does not have enough money to perform a withdraw
